caption:
To take care of others, you must first take care of yourself. 

That's why we’re offering 12 Days of Giveaways - to show our appreciation, spread some holiday cheer, and encourage you to take care of yourself during an exceptionally busy time of year.

Starting tomorrow through December 12th, we’ll reveal a carefully-curated @knackshops gift box each day. 

We asked you how you like to unwind after a shift, and each gift box features self-care products inspired by what you’ve shared with us.

Turn on your notifications so you get an alert every time we post something new, and make sure to enter each day for a chance to win. 

You don’t want to miss this. The fun starts tomorrow. 🎁
